      "name": "Shadow Essence",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Distilled from the Plane of Shadow, this oily substance imposes tenebrous effects. The enfeebled condition from shadow essence lasts for 24 hours.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span> Interact (Injury)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:29]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r {3d6}[negative]]]{3d6 negative damage} and [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r {3d6}[negative]]]{3d6 negative damage}, [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r {3d6}[negative]]]{3d6 negative damage}, [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage}, and enfeebled 2 (1 round)</p>"
        },
